Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:36.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}這就是與你的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:39.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Hello Mellow 甜美的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:47.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}今年也在尋求這份痛苦的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}酷暑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:22:01.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}僵硬的表情像是焦了的砂糖般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.79,0:22:07.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}與愛好甜食的你的糾結不斷重複
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:09.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}TEL...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:13.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}陰雨天的放學後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:19.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}「這樣如何」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:23.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}你惡作劇般地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:24.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}飄飄然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:29.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}短髮在風中搖曳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:33.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\an3}我們依然生活在孤獨的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:40.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4\an3}小聰明與固執都將轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:43.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}向著那顆星星前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:50.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}即使再度迎來能真心笑出來的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:54.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}無光也無暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:22:58.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}表裡都是你
